WEBVTT

00:00.016 --> 00:01.120
Previously on "Manifest"...

00:01.121 --> 00:03.140
His fingerprints were found
on the airplane?

00:03.141 --> 00:05.040
Inside the cargo hatch door.

00:05.050 --> 00:06.100
They were fresh
when the plane landed.

00:06.120 --> 00:08.080
There was a stowaway on 828.

00:08.090 --> 00:11.120
I want you to climb out onto
the landing gear and jump down.

00:11.130 --> 00:13.070
- And then what?
- And then you run.

00:13.090 --> 00:15.090
Olive is an amazing young woman.

00:15.100 --> 00:17.000
You've done an incredible job.

00:17.010 --> 00:18.180
It doesn't matter
where you found the strength.

00:18.200 --> 00:20.090
Save him.

00:20.100 --> 00:21.160
- Olive Stone?
- Yeah.

00:21.170 --> 00:23.140
I'm afraid we caught her shoplifting.

00:23.160 --> 00:25.040
- We need to go in.
- Are you crazy?

00:25.050 --> 00:26.120
You need to trust me, okay?

00:26.130 --> 00:28.040
But I thought
her dad was already here.

00:28.050 --> 00:29.070
There they are.

00:30.160 --> 00:32.159
Hi.
I'm Danny.

00:32.170 --> 00:35.020
NYPD!
Everybody down on the floor!

00:36.060 --> 00:37.120
Who made the call?

00:37.140 --> 00:39.050
I did.

00:39.060 --> 00:42.050
You don't have to take the fall
to protect me, Jared.

00:42.060 --> 00:44.010
That is the last thing that I want.

00:44.020 --> 00:46.090
Then tell me
what's really going on.

00:52.065 --> 00:53.965
- More water?
- No, thank you.

00:53.975 --> 00:57.005
- Can I get you anything?
- I'm fine.

00:57.015 --> 00:59.065
What about you, sir?

00:59.085 --> 01:01.005
Could I get a...

01:01.015 --> 01:02.965
I'll be right back.

01:06.045 --> 01:08.965
See anything interesting
down there, kiddo?

01:08.965 --> 01:10.895
No New York yet.

01:13.025 --> 01:16.975
This is the longest I've ever
been away from Cal.

01:16.985 --> 01:19.015
Well, Olive, being a twin

01:19.025 --> 01:21.945
is a heck of a special relationship.

01:21.955 --> 01:25.915
You always feel connected,
no matter where you are.

01:28.905 --> 01:31.015
- Did the trip work?
- I don't know what you're...

01:31.025 --> 01:35.065
Please. I can spot a marital
repair job a mile away.

01:35.075 --> 01:36.935
Oh.

01:36.945 --> 01:38.055
Ben and I are fine.

01:38.065 --> 01:39.995
I know my son.

01:40.015 --> 01:43.005
You two haven't been having
many good times lately.

01:46.895 --> 01:48.085
We're too focused on Cal.

01:49.935 --> 01:52.025
Getting away from the hospital helped.

01:52.035 --> 01:54.025
Maybe we're turning a corner.

